---
title: My drafts folder
permalink: /blog/drafts/
pageClass: pg-drafts
layout: layouts/page.njk
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<p>A public listing of things I'm thinking about writing about, presented in no particular order.</p>
<p>Any of these topics meaningful to you? Feel free to <a href="https://github.com/angeliquejw/dev-blog/issues/new?template=drafts.md" target="_blank">open an issue on GitHub</a> give me a shout on <a href="https://twitter.com/messypixels" target="_blank">Twitter</a>, as I'd love to hear your thoughts and could use the inspirational kick in the tush to move the post out of the purgatory that is my drafts folder.</p>

<ul>
{%- for post in drafts | sort(attribute="topic") %}

<li>
  <strong>{{ post.topic }}</strong>

  {%- if post.notes %}
  <p>{{ post.notes }}</p>
  {%- endif %}

  {%- if post.published %}
    <p>Now published &rarr; <a href="/blog/{{ post.published }}">{{ metadata.url }}/blog/{{ post.published }}</a></p>
  {%- endif %}

  {%- if post.links %}
  {%- set linksSize = post.links | length %}
    {%- if linksSize > 1 %}
      <ul class="u-list-reset">
        {%- for link in post.links %}
          <li><a href="{{ link.url }}">{{ link.url }}</a></li>
        {%- endfor %}
      </ul>
    {%- else %}
    <p><a href="{{ post.links.url }}">{{ post.links.url }}</a></p>
    {%- endif %}
  {%- endif %}
</li>

{%- endfor %}

</ul>

<a href="/blog/">Back to published posts</a>
